, it's really easy to find a better application. If you provide a service, you have the right to refuse service to anyone for any reason. We don't have to allow this invasion and we don't have to get ourselves in trouble with the law either.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 91, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASswfBqSY", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 66, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8687672, "raw_content": "", "author": "CleanUpPhillyTrump24", "created": 1781826828277, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "tomthung", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.aa.com.tr", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASswfBqSY.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.aa.com.tr/en/economy/cuba-approves-sweeping-economic-reforms-amid-deepening-crisis/3970970", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "OH Yeah the Boss just Liberated Cuba - had some free time between other POTUS duties", "last_comment_created": 1781835197203, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 66, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "Communist Party backs wider role for private capital as island struggles with power shortages, economic contraction and US pressure | Anadolu", "large_image": "MJlgOGqC